{
  "stem": "10588.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We couldn't go to ever to the universities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were-- we were always treated like second-class citizens as a general.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Though, it was not the official policy of the government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But in spite of it, my family managed to live there from 1600.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wonderful stories.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's ironic, because my grandmother lived through World War I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went through so much suffering that I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she still was-- she lost a brother before World War I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She lost-- She went through World War I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She lost two of her siblings, two of her children, and her little granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My uncle from England lost a four-year-old child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she never lost her faith in God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was constantly religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she used to tell me stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what were the [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How hard war was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How they became impoverished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And war is hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And ironically, when the Nazi Germany invaded Poland, when they came marching in, my grandmother baked a cake.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Itkala, ?] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carry it out for the poor soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't know they came to kill us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's not a question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard September 1, 1939, sirens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, airplanes were flying over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people started running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived not far from a street, which goes-- was the main street [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somebody had a-- a-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- I had two addresses in my childhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't remember the exact number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this one, I don't remember, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never knew that it's going be one day important, so I didn't memorize those things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or, maybe they didn't make any special impressions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember we started running to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
